  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/how-does-chinas-12th-five-year-plan-address-energy-and-environment">How does China‚Äôs 12th Five-Year Plan address energy and the environment?</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/4407552795_4083101675.jpg" alt="" title="" width="160" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-library-file-fid">
                <div class="field-content"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>The draft of China‚Äôs much-anticipated 12th Five-Year Plan was released this Saturday, March 5 at the opening session of the National People‚Äôs Congress (NPC).  The Plan will actually be brought to a vote at the close of the session later this week. While there may be some changes to the Plan, in past years these have not been large.</p></div>
  </div>
